00:01:12.063 --> 00:01:13.371
♪♪ Hi. Nima.

14
00:01:13.372 --> 00:01:14.371
Good morning. Aang.

15
00:01:14.372 --> 00:01:15.371
Oh. hello. Aang.

16
00:01:15.372 --> 00:01:22.371
♪♪

17
00:01:22.372 --> 00:01:24.371
Oh. perfect timing.

18
00:01:24.372 --> 00:01:26.371
I don't mind giving me a lift.

19
00:01:26.372 --> 00:01:28.371
Gyatso. this isn't the best time.

20
00:01:28.372 --> 00:01:30.371
I'm getting old. you know.

21
00:01:30.372 --> 00:01:32.391
My body doesn't move like it used to.

22
00:01:32.392 --> 00:01:34.411
I'm kind of in the middle of something.

23
00:01:34.412 --> 00:01:35.411
You are so heavy.

24
00:01:35.411 --> 00:01:37.391
Heavy? Me?

25
00:01:37.392 --> 00:01:39.391
I eat nothing but vegetables.

26
00:01:39.540 --> 00:01:41.391
Pie is not a vegetable.

27
00:01:41.392 --> 00:01:42.391
I'm gonna lose the race.

28
00:01:42.392 --> 00:01:44.391
Race? What race?

29
00:01:44.392 --> 00:01:46.391
We finally won!

30
00:01:46.392 --> 00:01:48.391
We won! We won!

31
00:01:48.416 --> 00:01:54.438
♪♪

32
00:01:54.463 --> 00:02:00.063
Aang. as an airbender. it's important
that you know when to show restraint.

33
00:02:00.421 --> 00:02:04.729
Even if you have the power
to win. you are the Avatar.

34
00:02:05.153 --> 00:02:10.930
A lot of people are going to rely on you.

35
00:02:20.867 --> 00:02:21.391
♪♪ He's gone!

36
00:02:21.392 --> 00:02:22.431
He ran away!

37
00:02:22.432 --> 00:02:24.431
What? I'm here!

38
00:02:24.432 --> 00:02:26.431
Where's the Avatar?

39
00:02:26.432 --> 00:02:27.431
Avatar!

40
00:02:27.432 --> 00:02:29.431
Aang. where are you?

41
00:02:29.432 --> 00:02:31.432
Gyatso. I'm here!

42
00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:37.452
♪♪ I'm right here!

43
00:02:37.453 --> 00:02:39.452
I'm here!

44
00:02:39.453 --> 00:02:41.452
I'm here!

45
00:02:41.453 --> 00:02:42.453
I'm here.

46
00:02:46.867 --> 00:02:48.452
[ Breathing heavily ] Hi. Momo.

47
00:02:49.302 --> 00:02:50.452
Hi. Appa.

48
00:02:50.552 --> 00:02:51.452
Was I asleep for long?

49
00:02:51.453 --> 00:02:52.452
Ooh! Okay. okay.

50
00:02:52.453 --> 00:02:54.472
I'm awake already.

51
00:02:54.473 --> 00:02:55.473
I know. I know.

52
00:02:55.722 --> 00:02:57.472
We've got a job to finish.

53
00:02:57.473 --> 00:02:58.473
[ Sighs ]

54
00:02:58.672 --> 00:03:00.472
Let's continue our journey.

55
00:03:00.847 --> 00:03:02.472
Back to our old home.

56
00:03:04.572 --> 00:03:12.472
♪♪

57
00:03:14.492 --> 00:03:22.492
♪♪

58
00:03:30.442 --> 00:03:32.492
♪♪

59
00:03:34.512 --> 00:03:42.512
♪♪

60
00:03:44.412 --> 00:03:49.512
♪♪

61
00:03:49.962 --> 00:03:51.512
This may not have been our best trip.

62
00:03:51.912 --> 00:03:54.532
but any Airbender relic we
find makes it all worthwhile.

63
00:03:56.432 --> 00:03:59.532
♪♪

64
00:04:00.582 --> 00:04:02.542
This could be the oldest
piece in our collection.

65
00:04:05.332 --> 00:04:09.533
♪♪ Sonam.

66
00:04:13.552 --> 00:04:21.552
♪♪

67
00:04:21.553 --> 00:04:24.552
[ Sighs ] I miss you.

68
00:04:27.202 --> 00:04:29.552
♪♪

69
00:04:30.590 --> 00:04:32.552
Momo. go outside with Appa.

70
00:04:34.123 --> 00:04:35.547
♪♪ Now!

71
00:04:44.358 --> 00:04:45.323
♪♪ Who are you?

72
00:04:45.348 --> 00:04:46.923
Why are you doing this?

73
00:04:50.523 --> 00:04:51.572
♪♪ Stop.

74
00:04:51.573 --> 00:04:53.572
I don't want to hurt you.

75
00:04:57.414 --> 00:04:57.890
♪♪ Where is it?

76
00:04:57.915 --> 00:04:58.458
Where is it?

77
00:04:58.622 --> 00:04:59.456
No. that's not it.

78
00:04:59.658 --> 00:05:01.156
Hey. those are antiques.

79
00:05:13.290 --> 00:05:14.359
[ Grunting ] ♪♪ Enough!

80
00:05:17.256 --> 00:05:18.123
♪♪ Wait!

81
00:05:18.255 --> 00:05:20.254
I found it!

82
00:05:20.279 --> 00:05:21.523
♪♪

83
00:05:21.548 --> 00:05:23.547
Sonam. why an after you?

84
00:05:42.842 --> 00:05:43.565
♪♪ ♪♪ Wait!

85
00:05:43.633 --> 00:05:46.632
♪♪

86
00:05:46.633 --> 00:05:48.632
No. that's 1.000 years old!

87
00:05:48.633 --> 00:05:54.865
♪♪

88
00:05:54.890 --> 00:05:56.632
Why don't we just talk? Maybe I can help.

89
00:05:56.633 --> 00:05:59.652
We don't need your help. Avatar.

90
00:05:59.653 --> 00:06:03.652
We're done living in a world where benders
have all the power and we have none.

91
00:06:03.653 --> 00:06:04.652
Who are you?

92
00:06:04.653 --> 00:06:05.652
We're the Denied.

93
00:06:05.653 --> 00:06:06.652
The Denied?

94
00:06:06.653 --> 00:06:08.652
Just kill him already!

95
00:06:08.653 --> 00:06:10.652
No! He'll bring the whole place down!

96
00:06:10.653 --> 00:06:15.652
♪♪

97
00:06:15.653 --> 00:06:18.672
[ Grunting ]

98
00:06:18.673 --> 00:06:22.672
♪♪

99
00:06:22.947 --> 00:06:24.672
[ Explosion ]

100
00:06:24.673 --> 00:06:29.672
♪♪

101
00:06:29.673 --> 00:06:31.672
[ Grunting ]

102
00:06:37.479 --> 00:06:39.000
♪♪ You saved me.

103
00:06:39.066 --> 00:06:40.692
♪♪

104
00:06:40.693 --> 00:06:43.692
Kallik. grab the map! Let's go!

105
00:06:57.718 --> 00:06:58.712
♪♪ ♪♪ Oh. no!

106
00:06:58.910 --> 00:07:06.712
♪♪

107
00:07:08.712 --> 00:07:16.712
♪♪

108
00:07:18.732 --> 00:07:26.732
♪♪

109
00:07:28.732 --> 00:07:36.733
♪♪

110
00:07:38.753 --> 00:07:46.753
♪♪

111
00:07:46.754 --> 00:07:52.753
♪♪

112
00:07:56.032 --> 00:07:57.026
I'm fine.

113
00:07:57.062 --> 00:07:58.828
Momo. I'm fine

114
00:07:58.853 --> 00:08:01.075
♪♪

115
00:08:01.823 --> 00:08:04.773
We've got to get to Republic City.

116
00:08:04.774 --> 00:08:06.773
Appa. yip. yip!

117
00:08:23.570 --> 00:08:24.793
♪♪ ♪♪ Water.

118
00:08:24.943 --> 00:08:31.793
Her tribes gather strength from
the moon and flow with the tides.

119
00:08:32.533 --> 00:08:36.532
Earth. a kingdom of unshakable will.

120
00:08:36.557 --> 00:08:38.793
Reliable and strong.

121
00:08:42.756 --> 00:08:43.813
♪♪ Fire.

122
00:08:43.814 --> 00:08:51.813
A nation capable of great
destruction. but also of great warmth.

123
00:08:51.814 --> 00:08:53.813
♪♪

124
00:08:53.814 --> 00:08:56.925
Air. peaceful nomads
with the power of a

125
00:08:56.926 --> 00:09:00.833
hurricane. but the
spirit of a gentle breeze.

126
00:09:00.834 --> 00:09:02.833
♪♪

127
00:09:02.834 --> 00:09:07.033
For generations. the
Avatar. the one master of

128
00:09:07.034 --> 00:09:11.833
all four elements. kept
the nations in balance.

129
00:09:12.408 --> 00:09:16.833
But when that responsibility
fell to me as a child. I ran away.

130
00:09:17.474 --> 00:09:19.833
I was caught in a deadly storm.

131
00:09:19.834 --> 00:09:26.853
but my Avatar spirit preserved me in a sphere
of energy where I stayed for 100 years.

132
00:09:27.182 --> 00:09:29.726
I woke to discover that
the balance preserved

133
00:09:29.727 --> 00:09:33.853
by the Avatar had
been destroyed by war.

134
00:09:34.675 --> 00:09:36.586
The air nomads were gone.

135
00:09:37.486 --> 00:09:38.853
All but one.

136
00:09:39.220 --> 00:09:40.220
Me.

137
00:09:41.035 --> 00:09:44.873
I could no longer run for my
responsibility as the Avatar.

138
00:09:45.834 --> 00:09:48.171
I found allies from every nation.

139
00:09:48.638 --> 00:09:51.873
Benders and non-benders.

140
00:09:52.750 --> 00:09:54.873
Katara taught me how to waterbend.

141
00:09:55.795 --> 00:09:57.873
Toph trained me in the
ways of the earthbenders.

142
00:09:59.023 --> 00:10:03.893
Zuko. once my worst enemy.
became my firebending teacher.

143
00:10:04.596 --> 00:10:08.893
Sokka showed me that bravery is the
most important part of being a leader.

144
00:10:10.048 --> 00:10:12.893
We became a family.

145
00:10:13.176 --> 00:10:16.893
And together. we ended
the Hundred Year War.

146
00:10:17.742 --> 00:10:22.913
Then. we began the hard
work of rebuilding the world.

147
00:10:25.913 --> 00:10:33.913
♪♪

148
00:10:33.914 --> 00:10:37.913
For so long. the nations
stood apart. alone.

149
00:10:38.262 --> 00:10:39.913
and we all suffered as a result.

150
00:10:40.662 --> 00:10:42.933
But here. on this ancient site.

151
00:10:43.082 --> 00:10:47.933
we created a place where all people are
welcome. bender and non-bender alike.

152
00:10:47.934 --> 00:10:51.933
working together in
peace to build the future.

153
00:10:51.934 --> 00:10:55.933
Though there are still those
who would seek to divide us.

154
00:10:56.332 --> 00:10:57.933
we remain united.

155
00:10:58.582 --> 00:10:59.933
As a council representative.

156
00:11:00.432 --> 00:11:04.953
I am honored to be here today celebrating
the anniversary of Republic City

157
00:11:05.027 --> 00:11:09.953
and the opening of Unity
Tower. a symbol for all people.

158
00:11:17.574 --> 00:11:18.920
♪♪ Yay!

159
00:11:18.954 --> 00:11:20.953
It's the Avatar!

160
00:11:32.258 --> 00:11:32.973
♪♪ Momo!

161
00:11:35.478 --> 00:11:36.854
[ Laughs ] Appa!

162
00:11:37.446 --> 00:11:39.516
I missed you. too. old friend.

163
00:11:41.274 --> 00:11:41.973
♪♪ Aang!

164
00:11:41.974 --> 00:11:43.973
Katara!

165
00:11:43.974 --> 00:11:45.993
♪♪

166
00:11:46.193 --> 00:11:47.559
[ Grunts ]

167
00:11:48.638 --> 00:11:49.659
You're hurt.

168
00:11:50.043 --> 00:11:53.993
♪♪

169
00:11:53.994 --> 00:11:56.993
♪♪

170
00:11:57.617 --> 00:11:58.993
Take a deep breath.

171
00:11:58.994 --> 00:12:03.993
[ Inhales deeply ] And exhale.

172
00:12:05.049 --> 00:12:07.185
I've heard the Denied
are growing in numbers.

173
00:12:07.318 --> 00:12:09.230
but they've never
done anything like this.

174
00:12:09.396 --> 00:12:11.013
Attacking the Avatar?

175
00:12:11.014 --> 00:12:12.014
Yeah.

176
00:12:12.562 --> 00:12:14.013
They were incredible fighters.

177
00:12:14.962 --> 00:12:16.013
even without bending.

178
00:12:17.353 --> 00:12:18.193
[ Grunts ] Oops!

179
00:12:18.218 --> 00:12:18.587
Ow!

180
00:12:18.612 --> 00:12:20.013
Breathe through it.

181
00:12:20.912 --> 00:12:22.617
Be honest. You're enjoying this.

182
00:12:22.717 --> 00:12:24.552
Aang. this is serious.

183
00:12:25.062 --> 00:12:27.667
Whatever this map they
took was. if they were willing to

184
00:12:27.668 --> 00:12:31.034
kill the Avatar to get it. what
else are they willing to do?

185
00:12:31.933 --> 00:12:32.961
I don't know.

186
00:12:33.935 --> 00:12:35.934
I'm worried about you.

187
00:12:36.383 --> 00:12:41.034
You're spending more and
more time at the Air Temple. alone.

188
00:12:41.732 --> 00:12:44.333
It's how I hold on to my past.

189
00:12:46.133 --> 00:12:49.054
I know how hard this is for you.

190
00:12:49.055 --> 00:12:51.054
[ Sighs ]

191
00:12:52.553 --> 00:12:54.054
When I was attacked.

192
00:12:54.702 --> 00:12:59.853
all I could think about
was that... this could be it.

193
00:13:00.635 --> 00:13:03.886
I'm the last Airbender.

194
00:13:04.727 --> 00:13:05.853
If I die.

195
00:13:06.610 --> 00:13:08.706
my culture dies with me.

196
00:13:11.573 --> 00:13:13.074
You may be the last Airbender.

197
00:13:14.023 --> 00:13:16.074
but you're not alone.

198
00:13:16.622 --> 00:13:19.973
Aang. none of this would exist without you.

199
00:13:21.323 --> 00:13:26.074
You made the city possible
with your heart and your mind.

200
00:13:26.765 --> 00:13:30.936
Because of you. all of the
nations live here. together.

201
00:13:31.728 --> 00:13:33.727
[ Sighs ]

202
00:13:33.993 --> 00:13:35.094
All except mine.

203
00:13:45.572 --> 00:13:49.573
I know. but the people here
still need your protection.

204
00:13:50.075 --> 00:13:52.074
You're an Airbender.

205
00:13:53.173 --> 00:13:55.074
but you're also the Avatar.

206
00:13:57.074 --> 00:13:59.074
You're right.

207
00:13:59.873 --> 00:14:04.094
Whoever this Sonam person
is. I need to find out more.

208
00:14:04.095 --> 00:14:07.094
♪♪

209
00:14:07.268 --> 00:14:15.094
♪♪

210
00:14:29.319 --> 00:14:30.414
♪♪ ♪♪ Aang.

211
00:14:30.722 --> 00:14:31.721
Avatar Roku.

212
00:14:31.879 --> 00:14:34.114
It is good to see you again.

213
00:14:34.348 --> 00:14:35.348
How can I help you?

214
00:14:35.471 --> 00:14:40.347
In your lifetime. did you ever hear of
an ancient Airbender named Sonam?

215
00:14:40.463 --> 00:14:44.134
I have not. but you have
many past lives to call upon.

216
00:14:45.083 --> 00:14:49.134
Perhaps one further back in
the Avatar cycle can help you.

217
00:14:49.808 --> 00:14:51.134
Thank you. Avatar Roku.

218
00:14:53.134 --> 00:14:56.134
-I'm sorry. -I've never heard of Sonam.

219
00:14:56.283 --> 00:14:58.134
-Perhaps earlier. -You must go find him.

220
00:14:58.135 --> 00:14:59.134
Not here. Not here.

221
00:14:59.135 --> 00:15:06.541
[ Indistinct conversation ]

222
00:15:08.641 --> 00:15:11.154
♪♪ Um. hello?

223
00:15:12.102 --> 00:15:13.853
Is there anyone here?

224
00:15:14.569 --> 00:15:15.920
Hello?

225
00:15:16.403 --> 00:15:18.154
[ Grunts ]

226
00:15:18.155 --> 00:15:23.174
Who calls upon Avatar Xian's
vast wealth of knowledge.

227
00:15:23.175 --> 00:15:25.174
♪♪

228
00:15:25.175 --> 00:15:26.656
[ Coughing ]

229
00:15:26.884 --> 00:15:28.378
Oh. hello.

230
00:15:28.403 --> 00:15:32.174
You look like an Avatar from
a time quite distant from mine.

231
00:15:32.373 --> 00:15:35.174
Please. please. tell me about your era.

232
00:15:35.175 --> 00:15:37.174
What are people wearing?

233
00:15:37.175 --> 00:15:38.215
Are sandals still a thing?

234
00:15:38.573 --> 00:15:40.174
Uh. yes.

235
00:15:40.573 --> 00:15:42.174
Why? Why?

236
00:15:42.273 --> 00:15:48.194
After so many years. open toes.
in someone else's crusty cuticles.

237
00:15:48.195 --> 00:15:49.194
Disgusting.

238
00:15:49.195 --> 00:15:50.195
Right.

239
00:15:50.591 --> 00:15:52.386
Anyway. I have come for your guidance.

240
00:15:52.469 --> 00:15:54.468
You see. I was attacked.

241
00:15:54.493 --> 00:15:56.194
It was not me. okay? It wasn't me.

242
00:15:56.195 --> 00:15:57.195
I know that.

243
00:15:57.893 --> 00:16:01.194
I think it might have something to
do with an Airbender named Sonam.

244
00:16:01.243 --> 00:16:04.194
Sonam. It sounds familiar.

245
00:16:05.093 --> 00:16:07.194
Sonam. Where have I heard that name before?

246
00:16:07.735 --> 00:16:10.366
Aha! Sonam was the youngest
daughter of the owner of

247
00:16:10.391 --> 00:16:12.480
the possum chicken shop
at the corner marketplace.

248
00:16:12.505 --> 00:16:15.214
Wait. That was my ex. Soniam.

249
00:16:15.496 --> 00:16:18.495
If only she didn't have
those humongous toenails.

250
00:16:18.520 --> 00:16:20.214
Ugh. Disgusting.

251
00:16:20.215 --> 00:16:21.214
This is going nowhere.

252
00:16:21.215 --> 00:16:22.214
Sonam?

253
00:16:22.548 --> 00:16:23.548
[ Sighs ]

254
00:16:24.143 --> 00:16:25.481
Well. thank you for your time.

255
00:16:26.076 --> 00:16:27.795
I must continue my search.

256
00:16:27.912 --> 00:16:29.814
Oh! Sonam!

257
00:16:30.080 --> 00:16:34.234
You're asking about the
legend of the lost Avatar.

258
00:16:34.552 --> 00:16:36.400
Sonam was an Avatar?

259
00:16:36.535 --> 00:16:37.793
Indeed she was.

260
00:16:37.946 --> 00:16:42.526
She was the Avatar in the
golden age of Airbenders.

261
00:16:42.660 --> 00:16:46.304
Legend said she had a staff
that could channel the vast energy

262
00:16:46.723 --> 00:16:51.569
of the spirit world. granting
its keeper unlimited power.

263
00:16:51.706 --> 00:16:52.428
Is --

264
00:16:52.936 --> 00:16:54.762
Is that even possible?

265
00:16:55.163 --> 00:16:56.874
We'll never know for sure.

266
00:16:57.340 --> 00:16:59.486
Many Avatars have tried
to communicate with her.

267
00:16:59.538 --> 00:17:00.287
but they couldn't.

268
00:17:00.555 --> 00:17:05.554
She disappeared so completely
that it was as if she never existed.

269
00:17:06.285 --> 00:17:07.495
And perhaps it's better that way.

270
00:17:08.362 --> 00:17:12.440
Maybe such a staff was too
dangerous for anyone to possess.

271
00:17:13.039 --> 00:17:14.449
Even the Avatar.

272
00:17:14.850 --> 00:17:17.274
But -- But that's exactly
why I need to find it.

273
00:17:17.722 --> 00:17:20.173
The people who attacked
me discovered a map.

274
00:17:20.274 --> 00:17:22.274
It must lead to the staff.

275
00:17:22.423 --> 00:17:24.274
Avatar Xian. please.

276
00:17:24.275 --> 00:17:26.274
You have to tell me where it is.

277
00:17:29.199 --> 00:17:35.295
The legend says that Sonam disappeared
with her staff on the peak of Mount Baihu.

278
00:17:37.594 --> 00:17:40.295
Katara. I'm sorry to leave so suddenly.

279
00:17:40.594 --> 00:17:43.295
but I found out what the Denied are after.

280
00:17:43.644 --> 00:17:46.275
Sonam had a staff of immense power.

281
00:17:46.424 --> 00:17:50.275
And in their hands. it could
be a devastating weapon.

282
00:17:50.276 --> 00:17:52.275
They have a head start.

283
00:17:52.276 --> 00:17:54.275
There's no time to waste.

284
00:17:54.275 --> 00:17:57.275
You take Appa and Momo and
gather up the rest of the team.

285
00:17:57.276 --> 00:17:59.275
We're gonna need some help.

286
00:18:05.295 --> 00:18:08.295
Next on the agenda. a
Fire Nation naval vessel

287
00:18:08.296 --> 00:18:12.295
came into conflict with an extremist
group of non-Benders called the Denied.

288
00:18:12.710 --> 00:18:15.162
They've been robbing
ancient sites -- Your Majesty!

289
00:18:15.693 --> 00:18:18.194
An urgent message has
arrived from Republic City.

290
00:18:18.296 --> 00:18:19.296
How impudent.

291
00:18:19.577 --> 00:18:22.459
Can't you see Fire Lord
Zuko is -- Chamberlain.

292
00:18:23.564 --> 00:18:25.340
There's only one person
who can send a message

293
00:18:25.364 --> 00:18:27.404
urgent enough to interrupt
the Fire Lord's counsel.

294
00:18:27.947 --> 00:18:28.926
Is it from the Avatar?

295
00:18:29.005 --> 00:18:30.005
Yes. my lord.

296
00:18:30.030 --> 00:18:30.659
Read it to me.

297
00:18:30.684 --> 00:18:31.684
Yes. my lord.

298
00:18:32.680 --> 00:18:34.081
[ Clears throat ]

299
00:18:34.756 --> 00:18:35.890
Um... [ Clears throat ]

300
00:18:36.316 --> 00:18:37.316
What are you doing?

301
00:18:37.415 --> 00:18:38.415
Read it quickly.

302
00:18:39.247 --> 00:18:40.648
Uh. y-y-yes. Grand Chamberlain.

303
00:18:41.078 --> 00:18:42.315
[ Clears throat ]

304
00:18:42.664 --> 00:18:45.335
Flameo Hotman. how's
ruling the Fire Nation.

305
00:18:45.336 --> 00:18:48.336
I hope the boring Chamberlain
you mentioned... [ Clears throat ]

306
00:18:48.384 --> 00:18:50.293
...in your letters isn't still...

307
00:18:50.797 --> 00:18:51.798
annoying you.

308
00:18:52.031 --> 00:18:54.743
Anywho. to cut to the
chase. I need your help.

309
00:18:55.209 --> 00:18:57.036
Can you please come immediately?

310
00:18:57.170 --> 00:19:00.748
Oh. and don't forget to
bring some firecracker buns.

311
00:19:00.915 --> 00:19:02.335
[ Sighs ]

312
00:19:03.534 --> 00:19:06.123
Allow me to present Sokka Cycle.

313
00:19:06.270 --> 00:19:10.355
Flames launch you into the sky where
you can drop water bombs on your enemies.

314
00:19:10.557 --> 00:19:13.355
Then skis pop out to
help you stick the landing.

315
00:19:13.454 --> 00:19:14.355
[ Laughs ]

316
00:19:14.356 --> 00:19:15.355
Pretty great. right?

317
00:19:15.356 --> 00:19:16.356
Eh. boring.

318
00:19:16.454 --> 00:19:18.355
Why would you need a sled
when you can just waterbend?

319
00:19:18.356 --> 00:19:19.355
Oh. oh. oh. like me. like me!

320
00:19:19.356 --> 00:19:21.355
Whee!

321
00:19:21.604 --> 00:19:24.375
Keep in mind. there's still plenty
of folks like me who can't bend.

322
00:19:24.376 --> 00:19:27.375
Why would Avatar Aang
partner with a non-bender?

323
00:19:27.987 --> 00:19:28.986
Why?

324
00:19:29.011 --> 00:19:29.802
I'll tell you why.

325
00:19:29.827 --> 00:19:31.375
I saved him from the iceberg.

326
00:19:31.376 --> 00:19:35.375
My boomerang flew by his side while I
parried away enemies with my trusty blade.

327
00:19:35.376 --> 00:19:39.820
I even took down the whole
Fire Nation airship armada.

328
00:19:40.869 --> 00:19:45.419
And on top of all that. I
was more popular than him.

329
00:19:45.444 --> 00:19:46.395
You're such a liar. Sokka.

330
00:19:46.496 --> 00:19:49.495
[ Birds chirping ]

331
00:19:49.823 --> 00:19:50.822
It's from the Avatar.

332
00:19:50.847 --> 00:19:51.846
Wow!

333
00:19:51.871 --> 00:19:52.871
Really?

334
00:19:52.896 --> 00:19:54.622
Oh. so now you think I'm cool?

335
00:19:54.647 --> 00:19:55.804
[ Laughter ]

336
00:19:56.356 --> 00:19:57.669
All right. metalbenders.

337
00:19:58.297 --> 00:19:59.960
Let's see if any of you tenderfoots

338
00:20:00.328 --> 00:20:02.024
can at least make me use my hands.

339
00:20:02.049 --> 00:20:05.048
[ Grunting ]

340
00:20:07.415 --> 00:20:15.415
♪♪

341
00:20:15.416 --> 00:20:17.415
[ Grunting ]

342
00:20:17.416 --> 00:20:20.415
♪♪

343
00:20:20.416 --> 00:20:21.416
[ Sighs ]

344
00:20:27.435 --> 00:20:35.435
♪♪

345
00:20:35.436 --> 00:20:39.435
I'm still the greatest
earthbender in the world!

346
00:20:39.502 --> 00:20:40.501
And I'm bored.

347
00:20:41.090 --> 00:20:43.644
M-Master Toph. there's a bird on your head.

348
00:20:43.669 --> 00:20:44.669
And?

349
00:20:44.884 --> 00:20:46.435
It looks like it has a message.

350
00:20:46.534 --> 00:20:47.534
Read.

351
00:20:48.304 --> 00:20:49.255
Uh. it's from Avatar Aang.

352
00:20:49.505 --> 00:20:50.505
He needs your help.

353
00:20:50.722 --> 00:20:51.622
It's the Denied?

354
00:20:51.951 --> 00:20:53.455
Where is he?

355
00:20:53.604 --> 00:20:55.455
Mount Baihu.

356
00:20:58.475 --> 00:21:06.475
♪♪

