♪♪ ♪♪ No. no. no!

361
00:21:58.922 --> 00:22:00.921
No.

362
00:22:01.253 --> 00:22:03.721
[ Sighs ]

363
00:22:04.022 --> 00:22:06.021
I love that hat.

